\[\cos \phi = \frac{3 \sqrt{148}}{148} \cdot \frac{\sqrt{148}}{\sqrt{148}} = \frac{3 \cdot \sqrt{148} \cdot \sqrt{148}}{148 \cdot \sqrt{148}} = \frac{3 \cdot 148}{148 \cdot \sqrt{148}} = \boxed{\frac{3}{\sqrt{148}}}.\]

